description.en:
SIAMESE NEKO is a community-driven token with daily active burns, rewards for holders, and donations to world wide causes. We provide 2% back to holders and 5% back to liquidity. We are meme token that is looking to challenge the world of dogs.

SIAMESE NEKO will power our NEKO exchange. Holding SIAMESE NEKO will give holders more opportunities in our eco-system. Holders will get access to discounts at retailers for their pets, staking, additional reward percentages, and reduction in fees while trading or swapping.
